node.text:
It was a pleasure to have had the chance to interview Aaron and pick his brain about his business successes, of which there are many! Over the past several years, we witnessed firsthand, the building of his great company and was absolutely crazy watching them take monster stride after monster stride as they did. Currently sitting at 144,000 followers strong on Insta and skies the limit for this talented and creative brand! Congratulations guys! @wootungsten . . .

Follow along as we take you in on the inside journey of Lip RipperZ inc, Product Brands Lip RipperZ and Bass Dynasty, written and narrated by our CEO himself Bryan Friedman @wolves_of_fishstreet. With no details held back! Welcome to the debut and first episode of Bass Dynasty TV. This is my life, and these are our people.
